{"tid":453621,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人一係嘈吵環境 隻耳就沙沙聲？","createTime":"2017-10-31T10:45:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-01T16:55:23.000Z","uid":53663,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ee7c66e348b96b92b557d0cd434d00d5453cfe7f","tid":453621,"uid":53663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T10:45:41.000Z","msg":"成日周圍啲人講野大野少少 或者我聽歌大聲少少 隻耳仔就會出現沙沙聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要揞住隻耳先舒服啲<br />\n由細到大都係咁 但覺得唔太嚴重所以一直都無理<br />\n依加開始覺得要正視問題 book星期六睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但依加好撚驚唔知會唔會好大獲 有無巴絲有試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c0d7dcaffa2ce30a421d61426164d72e6129d74","tid":453621,"uid":88396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T10:47:02.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n我都係咁<br />\n但唔知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3870ac818b9970b0f2783f24fcd7decb5cb8c5ad","tid":453621,"uid":53663,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T10:49:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名<br />\n我都係咁<br />\n但唔知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好唔方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成班fd開party吵吵鬧鬧咁 但我就要搵隻手揞住隻耳 如果唔係就覺得好似耳膜就穿咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6724dd0715a55a7b178805e1012b21d9a3c0ba8c","tid":453621,"uid":53663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T11:02:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8d2d9693c06131b681b886d453f91c71939a225","tid":453621,"uid":33438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T11:05:38.000Z","msg":"我都係咁 有時睇戲太大聲都會沙沙聲"},{"pid":"830344461b11c1890050f4519d2d582c153469d1","tid":453621,"uid":53663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T11:09:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係咁 有時睇戲太大聲都會沙沙聲</blockquote><br />\n巴打打算唔理？<br />\n上網見到有啲人都係無理到 後來過左好多年流埋鼻血 一check原來鼻咽癌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35c14868af8d4b5c28f6292e7005bf6bf2864ae2","tid":453621,"uid":73490,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T11:11:02.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過你根本唔係一個人 係一部電腦 沙沙聲代表你機械比人類干擾到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c634e2273a083140449cd75db9df8f674958a026","tid":453621,"uid":53663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T11:12:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇諗過你根本唔係一個人 係一部電腦 沙沙聲代表你機械比人類干擾到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n應該唔會掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d4c5ee169e84075b39143a2b839c5a20f036285","tid":453621,"uid":154062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T11:23:59.000Z","msg":"我，14年個陣試過耳水不平衡，左耳就開始咁樣，睇過政府耳鼻喉，做過聽力測試，用埋鼻鏡睇過有無鼻咽癌，都係無事...唔知點解咁....好灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95e5faea7cd2a29d2cc7b23556272d78d287e03e","tid":453621,"uid":53663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T11:32:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我，14年個陣試過耳水不平衡，左耳就開始咁樣，睇過政府耳鼻喉，做過聽力測試，用埋鼻鏡睇過有無鼻咽癌，都係無事...唔知點解咁....好灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上網都有個case係咁<br />\n患者情況同我一樣 但去檢查 醫生就話乜事都無 搞到佢都唔知點做好"},{"pid":"0b20d2cf97b862eb8bca0c12423268ef623da130","tid":453621,"uid":154062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T11:39