like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T02:41:40.000Z","msg":"我都係咁<br />\n巴打book左專科睇？"},{"pid":"203bbe4d5a013941529ce35dc5a6c010318ab174","tid":453621,"uid":140218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T02:46:30.000Z","msg":"中學嗰陣有<br />\n仲記得有人抆牛皮膠紙嗰時, 嚓一聲<br />\n跟住我隻耳好似沙沙聲漏風咁"},{"pid":"37e2e086c515e657c5cf6f4bec63d60f851f845c","tid":453621,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T03:05:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/耳鳴\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E8%80%B3%E9%B3%B4&d=NmQg4hzuelNsIzkRmOffeMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=ed2aaf6b\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/耳鳴</a>"},{"pid":"230a3d49d534c3afc234f3326dba097de6ae73c2","tid":453621,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T03:19:26.000Z","msg":"最常見的原因是因噪音引起的聽力喪失，其他原因則有耳部感染、罹患心血管疾病、美尼爾氏綜合症（俗稱耳水不平衡）、<span style=\"color: red;\">腦部腫瘤</span>、接觸特定藥物所致、頭部曾受傷過，以及耳屎；尤其常見於憂鬱症患者<br />\n<br />\n會唔會有蟲走咗入耳 或者 紅字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n症狀持續咗幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cf0415412d219070b7002ce937effc131bb588f","tid":453621,"uid":53663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T04:08:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最常見的原因是因噪音引起的聽力喪失，其他原因則有耳部感染、罹患心血管疾病、美尼爾氏綜合症（俗稱耳水不平衡）、<span style=\"color: red;\">腦部腫瘤</span>、接觸特定藥物所致、頭部曾受傷過，以及耳屎；尤其常見於憂鬱症患者<br />\n<br />\n會唔會有蟲走咗入耳 或者 紅字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n症狀持續咗幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌 咁撚大獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n持續左6 7年左右 我估係小學個陣出事 個陣成日都會遇到嘈吵嘅環境<br />\n依加平時係唔嘈環境都無問題 又唔會有頭痛 大病個啲 應該唔係腫瘤掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"769a2fedef03dfa2433ea060520940afeaea34e4","tid":453621,"uid":53663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T04:10:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/耳鳴\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E8%80%B3%E9%B3%B4&d=NmQg4hzuelNsIzkRmOffeMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=ed2aaf6b\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/耳鳴</a></blockquote><br />\n耳鳴係指外在環境沒發出聲音卻聽見聲音的一種狀況<br />\n<br />\n應該唔係耳嗚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 平時好靜我無事 係太嘈先有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}